  {
    "key": "14915fdccd57e2957d0741ad1086366e713439fba4a752cbed98326221f3bd53",
    "original": "{[img]gfx/ui/events/event_183.png[/img]{%oathtaker% the oathtaker joins you by the campfire. He nods.%SPEECH_ON%Respectfully, captain, I can say that it is a big ask to require a man to be of genuine goodness. When I first knew ya, I didn't think you had the chops for such an undertaking. I thought this world's creeping darkness would wither you away, grind you down like sand to a stone. But here you are. Stalwart. Keeping to the Oaths, one after the other. Good on ya. I think Young Anselm would be proud.%SPEECH_OFF%You thank the Oathtaker for the kind words.}",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"{[img]gfx/ui/events/event_183.png[/img]{%oathtaker% the oathtaker joins you by the campfire. He nods.%SPEECH_ON%Respectfully, captain, I can say that it is a big ask to require a man to be of genuine goodness. When I first knew ya, I didn't think you had the chops for such an undertaking. I thought this world's creeping darkness would wither you away, grind you down like sand to a stone. But here you are. Stalwart. Keeping to the Oaths, one after the other. Good on ya. I think Young Anselm would be proud.%SPEECH_OFF%You thank the Oathtaker for the kind words.}\""
  }
